{
  "stem": "19895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Well, in the borders of Budapest, there were military people and police were checking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I-- even so, if I was hiding my identity and I rolled away my coat and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They just wanted papers to see and then showing your identity, who you are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't have any to show.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was then turned back with the next of this group of people marching on the death march.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because thousands and thousands and thousands were following each other, day after day after day, new transports and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Eventually, I caught up with Tomas Stern, in the same place, at Harka.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I learned from him that in that moment when I was escaping, he tried the same thing, with no success.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And that's why even so if we were separated by our own attempts of escaping, we were together again, at the location of Harka.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some town people were just silently watching this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some places we were thrown food at, helping us, like a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people showed sympathy, by seeing that what a pitiful, sorry sight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not that they were against us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just watching it with silence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people laughing, some people pointing-- Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was different, which ever section of the town you went through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would not try to say that everybody was with hate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some were with pity and sorrow, and some helping with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we went to this town of [HUNGARIAN], that was a known place for a factory, which was making [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] canned food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were thrown by the town people some canned food, which they were-- and the guards didn't object to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
